name: Enki-Sankoré
body:
### Welcome to Enki-Sankoré
This is a new fork of Open-Sankoré, maintained by Enki company, based at Brazil. The objective is to have a product-ready application to use in digital boards, including the Enki board itself. 

### Open Source
We believe in open source and we will maintain this application as such.

### Authors and Contributors
All changes will be maintened by @gjalves and Enki company as GPL3+. The original Sankore version can be accessed here: http://open-sankore.org/

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out our [documentation](https://help.github.com/pages) or [contact support](https://github.com/contact) and we’ll help you sort it out.
